[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[1A\u001b[2K\u001b[G\u001b[1m\u001b[36mPreview\u001b[22m\u001b[32m my-saas\u001b[39m\u001b[2m a1b2c3d4...  12 messages\u001b[22m\r\n\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22mAll 5 tests passing.\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[2m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[32mYou: \u001b[22mNice. One more thing - can we add a retry mechanism? Sometimes the network request to refresh\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[32m     fails transiently\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[2m────────────────────────────────"]
[0.000, "o", "────────────────────────────\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2mAI:  \u001b[22mGood idea. I'll add exponential backoff retry for the refresh request.\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22mImplementation plan:\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m1. Retry up to 3 times with exponential backoff (1s, 2s, 4s)\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m2. Only retry on network errors and 5xx, not on 4xx (which means the token is actually invalid)\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m3. Queue concurrent refresh attempts so we don't send multiple refresh requests\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22mLet me implement this.\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[2m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[32mYou: \u001b[22mPerfect. Also make sure the UI doesn't flash a login screen during the retry\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[2m───────────────────────────"]
[0.000, "o", "─────────────────────────────────\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2mAI:  \u001b[22mDone. Added three things:\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m1. **Retry with backoff** in `auth/refresh.ts`:\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - 3 retries, exponential backoff (1s, 2s, 4s)\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - Only retries network errors and 5xx\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - Concurrent requests are queued (deduplication)\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m2. **Auth state buffer** in `auth/provider.tsx`:\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - New `refreshing` state prevents premature redirect to login\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - Shows a subtle loading indicator instead of flashing login page\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - 10-second timeout before giving up and showing login\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m3. **New tests**:\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - Test: retry succeeds on second attempt after network error\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - Tes"]
[0.000, "o", "t: no retry on 401 (invalid token)\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - Test: UI stays on current page during refresh retry\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m   - Test: UI redirects to login after timeout\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22mAll 9 tests passing. Want me to also add monitoring/alerting for failed refreshes?\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[2m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[32mYou: \u001b[22mNo, this is good enough for now. Let's ship it\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[2m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2mAI:  \u001b[22mAlright, here's a summary of all changes:\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m**Files modified:**\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m- src/auth/refresh.ts — Token rotation reorder + retry logic\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[2m     \u001b"]
